data.description: A great location, great lot, great layout, PLUS a great basement makes this house perfect for you. This 4 bedroom/2.5 bath house has been updated in all of the right spots- paint, flooring, kitchen, and baths. PLUS new roof and siding in 2024. Cozy family room with woodburning fireplace and built in bookshelves. Updated kitchen with painted grey cabinets, quartz counters, and stainless steel appliances. Large formal room is the perfect space for your personal needs- living room, office, dining room, or playroom. EXTRA large primary bedroom provides you all of the space you need in your private oasis. Remodeled primary bath boasts dual sink vanity plus large tile shower. The finished basement offers endless opportunities.  Relax on the weekends in the oversized fenced yard that is situated on a private cul-de-sac.  Only a 5 minute walk to popular Holland Park and close to all that downtown Fishers has to offer.
